transcript:
Customer: Hello.

Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hello. Vinod bhai aapka call disconnect ho gaya.
Executive: Aapne call kata tha?
Customer: Nahi maine nahi kata.
Executive: Mujhe laga aapne kata kyunki call kyunki call cut hua ekdum se toh mere ko laga aapne kata.
Customer: Nahi nahi yaar mujhe meeting schedule karna tha.
Customer: Jyada time nahi lunga main usme woh update karake aur bylead consume karana hai mujhe. Yeh saari cheeze.
Executive: Karwane ke liye time dekho yaar 3 baj rahe hai abhi toh. 3:30 ho rahi hai.
Customer: Toh kab connect karein phir?
Executive: Hmm?
Customer: Kab connect karein?
Executive: Abhi toh dekho main bahar aa rakha hu. Toh abhi bilkul bhi nahi hoga. Kal hi ho payega phir.
Customer: Ek kaam karo phir kal ka rehne do aap kal toh Saturday ho jayega phir Monday hi hoga phir toh.
Executive: Ji. Monday hoga. Toh bylead ka connection consume kar lenge Vinod bhai abhi aap dekh lijiye.
Executive: Bylead dekho consume toh karu lekin consume karne ke liye kuch hona bhi chahiye na. Abhi dekho aap bhale isme check kar lo usme aapko dikha dega ki matlab consume karne ke liye bylead hai hi nahi usme.
Customer: Main wahi toh bol raha hu tumko abhi dikha dunga kis tarike se aapko filter lagana hai, kaise bylead consume karna hai. Isliye toh main bol raha hu.
Executive: Woh toh hai lekin abhi dekho main hu bahar toh na toh phone pe kar sakta hu na kuch.
Customer: Chaliye ek baar filter karke na bylead zarur consume kar lijiye zara kyunki bylead lapse ho raha hai aapka.
Executive: Lapse toh ho raha hai lekin bylead bhi consume karne ke liye maine pichli baar bhi aapko bataya dekho byleads hoti hai toh main saari consume kar leta hu lekin agar ab kuch useful hi nahi hai toh 50 kg 10 kg mein waise bylead lene ka bhi matlab nahi hai.
Customer: Woh aapko filter laga ke consume karna hai na filter maine aapko bataya tha na kaise.
Executive: Haan ji filter laga ke hi filter lagane ke baad bhi waisa hai ki hai nahi bylead use karne layak toh isliye.
Customer: Toh aap past lead mein jaake check kiya aapne jo maine past lead dikhai thi aapko waha pe aapko yeh feedback wagera show karega.
Executive: Haan haan.
Customer: Woh aap ek baar feedback ki jo jagah hai waha pe ki aapko yeh bylead chahiye aur isme aapko aa raha hai toh fold down ho raha hai. Toh maine feedback aapko dikhaya tha.
Customer: Theek hai?
Executive: Hmm.
Customer: Monday mein ek baar connect karke dobara isko update kara deta hu.
Executive: Aur time pe karna thoda abhi kal bhi kal bhi aapne matlab 3 baje ke aas pass phone kiya tha aaj bhi 3 baje ke aas pass kya 1 baje ka matlab.
Customer: Kitne baje kitne baje call karunga?
Executive: Matlab agar 1 baje bolo toh 1 baje hi kar do matlab aisa keh raha hu matlab 3 baje kar rahe ho kyunki abhi mere ko koi kaam hota hai toh main itna time toh wait karunga nahi matlab.
Customer: Chaliye theek hai main 1 baje hi connect karta hu.
Executive: Haan toh 1 baje matlab 1 baje hi kar lena kyunki main thoda free hoke bhi kar saku kyunki time nikal lu warna phir aap 3 baje karte toh 3 baje main abhi kuch alag kaam mein hu toh isliye.
Customer: Theek hai theek hai main.
Executive: Hmm theek hai.
summary:
Concerns:

- Wants to update and consume buyleads.

- Byleads are lapsing.

- Wants the executive to call at 1 PM.



Resolution:

- Executive said he is currently out.

- Executive will connect on Monday at 1 PM.

- Executive explained how to check past leads.



Next Steps: 

- Executive will connect on Monday at 1 PM.



Alert (If Any):

None

- Neutral -> Neutral
